packages <- c("rgdal", "dplyr", "zoo", "RColorBrewer", "viridis", "plyr", "digitize", "jpeg", "devtools", 
    "imager", "dplyr", "ggplot2", "ggridges", "ggjoy", "ggthemes", "svDialogs", "data.table", "tibble",

    install.packages(packages, dependencies = T)
    require(packages)
}
